d_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A163">Non-Governmental Organization (Non-profit)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A37">Individual</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A167">Faith-Based Organization</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-resources field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Resources</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-case-budget field-type-number-decimal field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Total Budget:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-case-budget-annual field-type-number-decimal field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Average Annual Budget:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">US$50 000.00</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-staff-full-time field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Number of Full-Time Staff:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">6</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-staff-part-time field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Number of Part-Time Staff:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">12</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-staff-type field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Staff Type:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">The part time staff were employs of the city that were lent to the PB organization</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-volunteers field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Number of Volunteers:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">150</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>      </div>
